OL,3,CTrial date set for 14-year-old boy
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy charged with murder
OL,7,Fhas appeared in court after a female
OL,8,Fbody was found in Blaina, near Ebbw
OL,9,FVale, on Monday 22 June.
OL,11,FThe body has still not been formally
OL,12,Fidentified but police believe it to be
OL,13,F14-year-old Lilly Jones, who was
OL,14,Freported missing having last been seen
OL,15,Fon Saturday 20 June.
OL,17,FThe boy from the Blaenau Gwent area,
OL,18,Fwho cannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,19,Fappeared in Cardiff Crown Court on
OL,20,FMonday 29 June for a hearing that
OL,21,Flasted 21 minutes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
