PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782904687
OL,3,CTrial date set for 14-year-old boy
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FHe spoke only to confirm his name,
OL,7,Fdate of birth and address. He was
OL,8,Faccompanied by his mother who sat
OL,9,Fbehind the dock and was visibly upset.
OL,11,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,12,FRecorder of Cardiff, has fixed a trial
OL,13,Fdate beginning on 23 November, which
OL,14,Fis estimated to last four weeks.
OL,16,FA plea and trial preparation hearing
OL,17,Fhas been set for 24 July.
OL,19,FThe defendant was remanded into secure
OL,20,Fyouth accommodation until his next
OL,21,Fcourt appearance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
