PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782904687
OL,3,CTrial date set for 14-year-old boy
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,FLilly Jones was a student at Brynmawr
OL,7,FFoundation School.
OL,9,FFollowing the news that a body,
OL,10,Fbelieved to be Lilly's, had been
OL,11,Fdiscovered, Head teacher Gerard
OL,12,FMcNamara said in a statement: "We are
OL,13,Fdeeply saddened to hear of the tragic
OL,14,Fpassing of one of our pupils, Lilly
OL,15,FJones.
OL,17,F"She was a valued member of our school
OL,18,Fcommunity, known for her kindness,
OL,19,Fwarmth, and bubbly personality.
OL,26,@tD@_OUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
