CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1782904687
OL,3,CTrial date set for 14-year-old boy
OL,4,Ccharged with murder
OL,6,F"Her loss will be felt profoundly by
OL,7,Fstudents, staff, and all who knew her.
OL,9,F"Our thoughts and heartfelt
OL,10,Fcondolences are with her family,
OL,11,Ffriends, and loved ones during this
OL,12,Fincredibly difficult time.
OL,14,F"The school is providing support to
OL,15,Fpupils and staff who have been
OL,16,Faffected, and we are working closely
OL,17,Fwith relevant agencies to ensure that
OL,18,Fhelp is available to anyone who needs
OL,19,Fit."
